(68, '2', '\r\n            Train the mind to train the brain to train the mind!\r\n          ', 1, 'Demo User', '\r\n            We can train our mind in a way so that it can change our brain.\r\n\r\n\r\n          ', 'False. Brains and Minds are the same\r\n', '\r\n            Imagine that your child is melancholic all the time. What would you do to change his/her general\r\n            nature?\r\n\r\n          ', ' Tell him/her to look at the bright side of life', '2021-06-06 06:28:43'),
(69, '3', '\r\n            Introducing the Brain-Mind Concept to the children\r\n          ', 1, 'Demo User', '\r\n            Neuroplastic changes stop at what age?\r\n\r\n\r\n          ', 'It never stops but slows down gradually\r\n', '\r\n            Your child returns from school and shares that he/she has been bullied and doesnt want to go back\r\n            tomorrow. What would you', 'Tell him/her to fight with the bullies', '2021-06-06 06:48:13'),
(70, '4', '\r\n            How to deal with suffering and usher in happiness amidst adversities\r\n          ', 1, 'Demo User', '\r\n            What is the best way to face a challenge or a negative situation?\r\n\r\n\r\n          ', 'Let time solve the problem\r\n', '\r\n            Your child has not completed a homework and doesnt want to go to school for the fear of being\r\n            scolded. What should you do?', 'Let them skip school', '2021-06-06 06:49:32'),
(71, '5', '\r\n            Changes in current education system\r\n          ', 1, 'Demo User', '\r\n            How can we focus on essential socio-emotional development in young students?\r\n\r\n\r\n          ', 'By taking more standardized tests', '\r\n            As a parent, which of school would you want your child to be in?\r\n\r\n          ', 'A school where discipline is the law\r\n', '2021-06-06 06:51:25'),
